{"id":1665483,"retrievedAt":"2026-04-08T12:15:03.736Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"","id":1665483,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"AI & Animals: A documentary","overview":"hile AI's impact on humanity dominates headlines, its effects on billions of animals receives virtually no attention. We are at a crossroads. AI will significantly impact the lives of animals — for better or worse. Animal advocates face an urgent choice: react after harm is done, or prevent catastrophe before it unfolds. History shows us the cost of being reactive. We failed to prevent factory farming before it became entrenched. We failed to stop industrial fish farming before billions suffered. We failed to anticipate insect farming's explosive growth. With AI, we cannot afford to make the same mistake.  AI & ANIMALS brings together 16 of the world's leading voices on AI and animal advocacy — ethicists, scientists, strategists and technologists from Princeton, NYU, LSE, and beyond — to explore what's at stake, and what we can do about it.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/v1j464wg64k8v49tEoJKQ5TkIhL.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":294654,"logo_path":null,"name":"Animal Ethics","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","name":"United States of America"}],"release_date":"2026-03-02","revenue":0,"runtime":36,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"AI & Animals: A documentary","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":556159,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Peter Singer","original_name":"Peter Singer","popularity":0.3502,"profile_path":"/cGCczFAU0OWXLpENZ7GwCtq1Ojt.jpg","cast_id":1,"character":"","credit_id":"69d53ce45ed0aac92407143b",